+# The Anatomy of a Single Post: How Executive Narrative Shifts Drain Real-World Capital
+
+This document outlines the systematic microstructure breakdown that occurred on June 11, 2026, demonstrating how a single social media post can simultaneously manipulate global equity indices, international energy commodities, and decentralized prediction markets to strip wealth from non-institutional participants.
+
+## 1. The Microstructure Sequence (June 11, 2026)
+
+The market action followed a coordinated, multi-tier volatility trap engineered through unverified executive communications:
+
+* **09:30 AM (The Morning Threat):** A social media post threatening imminent military action spiked Brent and WTI crude oil futures, while dragging the Dow Jones Industrial Average down significantly. Retail traders buying protection (Puts) or positioning for a prolonged geopolitical escalation locked into hyper-inflated Implied Volatility (IV) premiums.
+* **02:00 PM (The Afternoon Reversal):** A sudden follow-up post announced the absolute cancellation of scheduled military strikes. Within minutes, the Dow surged **700+ points**, West Texas Intermediate (WTI) crude plunged **3% down to $87 a barrel**, and short-dated options premiums were instantly crushed.
+
+```
+┌────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐
+│  TRUMP SOCIAL POST VOLATILITY TIMELINE: JUNE 11, 2026                 │
+├────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┤
+│                                                                        │
+│  [09:30 AM] Threat Posted ──► Oil Spikes 3% / Equities Tank            │
